import React from 'react' const Human = () => { return (

Human Error

Problems:

1. Amp validation failed

2. Story under violation

3. Story under moderation

4. Images not uploaded

5. The same video shows multiple times in the video slider

6. Content missing in article

7. Tags showing on frontend

8. Bylines are missing

9. Story not reflected in cms

10. Article not appearing in feed





Solutions:

1. Checked text view and suggest changes if any

2. Checked if user had made mistake while copy pasting content

3. Ask to reupload videos in case of under moderation

4. Ask to resize images in case of upload issues

5. Ask to republish story if they failed to do correctly
) } export default Human;
